llow%20to%20the%20site%20near%20the%20airport%20highway%20where%20Nasrallah%20will%20be%20buried.%20Safieddine%20will%20be%20interred%20in%20his%20southern%20hometown%20of%20Deir%20Qanun%20al-Nahr%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Hezbollah%20official%20Ali%20Daamoush%20told%20reporters%20Saturday%20that%20about%20800%20personalities%20from%2065%20countries%20will%20be%20attending%20the%20funeral%20in%20addition%20to%20thousands%20of%20individuals%20and%20activists%20from%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCome%20from%20every%20home%2C%20village%20and%20city%20so%20that%20we%20tell%20the%20enemy%20that%20this%20resistance%20will%20stay%20and%20is%20ready%20in%20the%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20Daamoush%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeople%20Mourn%20Leader%20'Dearest%20to%20Soul'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENasrallah%20was%20Hezbollah's%20leader%20for%20more%20than%2030%20years%20and%20one%20of%20its%20founders.%20He%20enjoyed%20wide%20influence%20among%20Iran-backed%20groups%20in%20the%20region%20and%20was%20widely%20respected%20in%20the%20so-called%20Iran-led%20axis%20of%20resistance%20that%20included%20Iraqi%2C%20Yemeni%20and%20Palestinian%20factions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIranian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Araghchi%2C%20in%20a%20speech%20from%20Beirut%2C%20described%20the%20dead%20leaders%20as%20%26quot%3Btwo%20heroes%20of%20the%20resistance%26quot%3B%20and%20vowed%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20path%20of%20resistance%20will%20continue%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20mourners%2C%20Umm%20Mahdi%2C%2055%2C%20who%20had%20come%20%26quot%3Bto%20see%20him%20(Nasrallah)%20one%20last%20time%20and%20see%20his%20shrine%26quot%3B%20told%20AFP%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20feel%20sadness%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20least%20we%20can%20do%20for%20Sayyed%20who%20gave%20up%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%20using%20an%20honorific.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20attendee%20Khouloud%20Hamieh%2C%2036%2C%20told%20AFP%20she%20came%20from%20the%20east%20to%20mourn%20the%20leader%20she%20said%20was%20%26quot%3Bdearest%20to%20our%20souls%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20feeling%20is%20indescribable%2C%20my%20heart%20is%20beating%20(so%20fast)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20her%20eyes%20filled%20with%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20cold%20weather%20and%20large%20crowds%2C%20she%20said%20she%20would%20not%20have%20missed%20the%20funeral%20for%20anything.%20%26quot%3BEven%20if%20we%20had%20to%20crawl%20to%20get%20here%2C%20we%20would%20still%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESahar%20al-Attar%2C%20a%20mourner%20who%20travelled%20from%20Lebanon's%20Bekaa%20valley%20for%20the%20funeral%20told%20Associated%20Press%20she%20still%20%26quot%3Bcannot%20believe%20what%20happened.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20have%20come%20even%20under%20bullets%26quot%3B%20to%20attend%20Nasrallah's%20burial%2C%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20an%20indescribable%20feeling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHezbollah's%20call%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20has%20been%20calling%20on%20its%20supporters%20to%20attend%20the%20funeral%20in%20large%20numbers%20in%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20move%20to%20show%20that%20the%20group%20remains%20powerful%20after%20suffering%20major%20blows%20during%20a%2014-month%20war%20with%20Israel%20that%20left%20many%20of%20its%20senior%20political%20and%20military%20officials%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20US-brokered%20ceasefire%20deal%20that%20ended%20the%20war%20with%20Israel%20on%20November%2027%2C%20Hezbollah%20is%20not%20supposed%20to%20have%20an%20armed%20presence%20along%20the%20border%20with%20Israel.%20Hezbollah's%20rivals%20have%20been%20calling%20on%20the%20group%20to%20lay%20down%20its%20weapons%20all%20over%20Lebanon%20and%20become%20a%20political%20faction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIsraeli%20Strike%3C%2Fs