0Saturday.%20Water%20in%20the%20tunnel%20and%20silt%20are%20making%20the%20rescue%20operation%20challenging%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElectricity%20supply%20to%20the%20tunnel%20has%20been%20restored%2C%20they%20said%2C%20adding%20they%20are%20also%20supplying%20oxygen%20to%20the%20trapped%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelangana%20Minister%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%2C%20who%20came%20to%20the%20affected%20site%20to%20take%20stock%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20told%20NDTV%20the%20tunnel%20has%20been%20under%20construction%20for%20the%20last%2020%20years.%20It%20is%20a%2044-km-long%20tunnel%20and%20when%20completed%20will%20supply%20water%20to%20about%20four%20lakh%20acres%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20small%20leak%20became%20a%20huge%20gap%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20tunnel%20and%20water%20and%20mud%20rushed%20in%2C%20flooding%20the%20tunnel...%20We%20have%20been%20working%20round%20the%20clock.%20We%20have%20sought%20help%20from%20the%20army%20and%20the%20navy%20for%20divers%2C%20and%20the%20NDRF%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Reddy%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20workers%20were%20injured%20when%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20roof%20of%20the%20tunnel%20being%20dug%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Srisailam%20Left%20Bank%20Canal%20(SLBC)%20collapsed.%20Seventy%20people%20were%20working%20inside%20the%20tunnel%20when%20the%20roof%20collapsed%20for%20three%20meters%20at%20the%2014-km%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20have%20come%20out%2C%20the%20remaining%20eight%20remained%20trapped.%20They%20include%20two%20engineers%20and%20two%20machine%20operators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDRF%20team%2C%20which%20reached%20up%20to%2011%20km%2C%20found%20water%20and%20mud%20beyond%20that%20point.%20The%20rescue%20workers%20walked%20for%20another%202.5%20km%20to%20reach%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENagarkurnool%20district%20Collector%20Badavath%20Santosh%20said%20the%20efforts%20are%20being%20made%20for%20removing%20water%20and%20silt%20for%20the%20rescue%20team%20to%20move%20forward.%20The%20team%20was%20unable%20to%20take%20heavy%20equipment%20near%20the%20site%20of%20the%20roof%20collapse%20due%20to%20water%20and%20silt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trapped%20men%20are%20from%20Jharkhand%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Punjab%2C%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinisters%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%20and%20Jupally%20Krishna%20Reddy%20held%20a%20meeting%20with%20officials%20of%20the%20NDRF%2C%20the%20army%2C%20and%20other%20agencies%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20A%20Revanth%20Reddy%20expressed%20shock%20over%20the%20tunnel%20accident%2C%20and%20assured%20the%20government%20would%20extend%20all%20possible%20help.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Saturday%20spoke%20to%20Mr%20Reddy%20over%20phone%2C%20and%20asked%20about%20the%20matter.%20PM%20Modi%20also%20assured%20all%20support%20from%20the%20central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740307080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fc9bfvjeg_tunnel_625x300_23_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftelangana-news%2Fvideo-inside-telangana-tunnel-where-roof-collapsed-8-workers-trapped-7775900%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Footage%20from%20inside%20the%20tunnel%20in%20Telangana%20whose%20roof%20collapsed%20while%20construction%20work%20was%20going%20on%20showed%20debris%20stuck%20inside%20with%20little%20space%20left%20to%20bypass%20the%20blocked%20part.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Samay%20jokes%20with%20Tanmay%20amid%20India's%20Got%20Latent%20row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740307065000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118503408%2Cimgsize-1021643.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fsamay-raina-jokes-with-tanm