%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPlus%2C%20it's%20an%20excellent%20time%20to%20get%20into%20the%20business%20of%20business.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20never%20been%20a%20better%20time%20to%20be%20an%20entrepreneur%2C%26quot%3B%20Sabatier%20declares%20in%20his%20latest%20book%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penguinrandomhouse.com%2Fbooks%2F723308%2Finner-entrepreneur-by-grant-sabatier%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EInner%20Entrepreneur%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20he%20describes%20as%20a%20blueprint%20he's%20designed%2C%20having%20launched%20seven%20businesses%2C%20acquired%20three%2C%20and%20sold%20one.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBI%20spoke%20to%20the%20entrepreneur%2C%20whose%20latest%20venture%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fclintonvillebooks.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ean%20independent%20bookstore%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20he%20opened%20in%20the%20Clintonville%20neighborhood%20of%20Columbus%2C%20about%20why%20the%20time%20is%20ripe%20for%20entrepreneurship%20and%20what%20businesses%20he%20would%20build%20if%20he%20had%20to%20start%20from%20scratch.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227f0e546c-a489-4f50-b0b4-dc08c9437eb8%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20barriers%20to%20entry%20have%20never%20been%20lower%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20a%20lot%20easier%20and%20cheaper%20to%20start%20a%20business%20in%202025%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BBefore%2C%20you%20had%20to%20really%20stop%20and%20figure%20out%20everything%20and%20maybe%20apprentice%20or%20put%20down%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20and%20take%20a%20big%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sabatier.%20%26quot%3BBut%20now%20there%20are%20just%20so%20many%20blueprints%20available%20and%20so%20many%20ways%20to%20learn.%20Really%20successful%20entrepreneurs%20are%20sharing%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20they%20ever%20have%2C%20so%20as%20knowledge%20has%20been%20more%20democratized%20the%20barrier%20is%20just%20a%20lot%20lower.%20You%20can%20evaluate%20a%20business%20idea%20with%20a%20lot%20more%20information%20than%20you%20ever%20could%20have%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20misconceptions%20about%20entrepreneurship%20is%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Bsuper%20risky%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20argue%20that%20having%20a%20full-time%20job%2C%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20is%20often%20riskier%20than%20having%20a%20business%20that%20you%20built%20yourself.%20Because%2C%20at%20least%20with%20your%20own%20business%2C%20you%20can%20control%20more%20of%20the%20variables%20than%20if%20you're%20working%20for%20someone%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20also%20cheaper%20to%20start%20and%20scale%20a%20business%20than%20it%20ever%20has%20been.%20If%20you're%20starting%20with%20consulting%2C%20which%20is%20how%20Sabatier%20began%20his%20entrepreneurial%20journey%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20really%20don't%20need%20much%20money%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20might%20need%20a%20website%2C%20which%20you%20can%20now%20put%20up%20using%20AI%20for%20like%20%2415%2C%20and%20you%20can%20set%20up%20social%20media%20profiles%20for%20free.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2268ed195f-f826-45db-9333-7e764983f4b5%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20he%20would%20do%20if%20he%20had%20to%20start%20from%20scratch%20in%202025%3A%20Lean%20into%20AI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUntil%20Sabatier%20opened%20Clintonville%20Books%2C%20which%20he%20considers%20%26quot%3Bmore%20as%20an%20investment%20in%20my%20neighborhood%20and%20in%20my%20happiness%20than%20as%20a%20capital%20investment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20exclusively%20built%20and%20scaled%20online%20businesses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22clintonville%20books%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b8ef7ac040bd1b4ca2dc1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221868%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESabatier%20opened%20Clintonville%20Books%20in%20November%202024.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Grant%20Sabatier%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20he%20lost%20everything%20and%20had%20to%20start%20over%20in%202025%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20definitely%20learn%20how%20to%20build%20different%20AI%20agents%20and%20use%20them%20to%20code%20software%20products%20and%20different%20AI%20tools%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20predicts%20it%20would%20be%20easier%20to%20get%20started%20than%20it%20was%20in%202010%20when%20he%20got%20laid%20off%20from%20his%209-to-5%20and%20tried%20entrepreneurship%20out%20of%20necessity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20build%20websites%20from%20scratch.%20You%20can%20now%20use%20AI%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20build%20websites%2C%20and%20within%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20you%20can%20build%20a%20simple%20platform%20and%20then%20build%20a%20tool%20that%20ideally%20has%20a%20subscription%20component%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20launching%20an%20AI%20company%20feels%20daunting%2C%20a%20more%20manageable%20first%20step%20is%20to%20learn%20about%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20how%20it%20works%2C%20and%20how%20you%20can%20leverage%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BSkills%20are%20future%20currency.%20Skills%20are%20ultimately%20what%20allow%20you%20to%20adapt%20and%20build%20resilience%2C%20and%2C%20as%20we%20know%2C%20the%20world's%20just%20changing%20faster%20than%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20emphasizing%20that%20if%20he%20were%20to%20add%20one%20skill%20to%20his%20repertoire%20today%2C%20it%20would%20be%20AI.%20%26quot%3BDo%20your%20best%20to%20stay%20up%20to%20date%20on%20it.%20It's%20impossible%20to%20keep%20track%20of%