-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia's%2010-for-1%20split%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20granted%20each%20shareholder%20an%20additional%20nine%20shares%2C%20while%20its%20price%20went%20from%20about%20%241%2C210%20apiece%20to%20about%20%24121.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20stock%20price%20to%20climb%20high%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%20it%20usually%20has%20to%20have%20seen%20significant%20upside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStocks%20usually%20split%20after%20a%20consistent%20run%20of%20strong%20performance.%20Since%201980%2C%20companies%20that%20split%20have%20returned%2028.4%25%20annually%20for%20five%20years%20before%20their%20announcement%20with%20an%20average%2067%25%20return%20in%20the%20year%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bank%20said%20in%20a%20client%20note%20authored%20by%20Jared%20Woodard%2C%20an%20investment%20%26amp%3B%20ETF%20strategist%20at%20BofA%20Securities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20outperformance%20usually%20continues%20after%20the%20split%2C%20the%20bank%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20a%20split%20is%20announced%2C%20stocks%20have%20notched%2025%25%20total%20returns%20in%20the%20subsequent%2012%20months%2C%20compared%20to%2012%25%20for%20the%20broad%20index%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20note%20continued.%20%26quot%3BSplits%20in%202024%20are%20on%20track%20to%20outpace%20historical%20norms%2C%20with%20the%20average%20stock%20up%2017%25%20in%20the%206%20months%20after%20their%20split.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20other%20factors%20are%20at%20play.%20If%20the%20macroeconomic%20picture%20is%20poor%2C%20stocks%20that%20split%20can%20still%20underperform.%20For%20example%2C%20as%20inflation%20soared%20in%202022%2C%20prompting%20Fed%20rate%20hikes%20and%20a%20bear%20market%20for%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20several%20stocks%20that%20split%20floundered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompanies%20like%20Amazon%2C%20Google%2C%20Tesla%2C%20and%20Dexcom%20struggled%20in%20the%2012%20months%20after%20splits%20were%20announced%20in%202022%20as%20interest%20rates%20spiked%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20note%20said.%20%26quot%3BMore%20recently%2C%20Super%20Micro%20Computer%20is%20down%20about%2050%25%20since%20its%20split%20announcement%20in%20August%202024.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20note%2C%20the%20bank%20identified%20a%20list%20of%20stocks%20with%20share%20prices%20above%20%24500%20%E2%80%94%20the%20most%20expensive%208%25%20of%20stocks%20%E2%80%94%20making%20them%20prime%20candidates%20to%20split%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%2C%20we've%20included%20those%20on%20the%20list%20that%20Bank%20of%20America%20has%20also%20assigned%20a%20%26quot%3BBuy%26quot%3B%20rating.%20Performance%20over%20the%20last%2012%20months%20is%20also%20included.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENVR%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221654%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22nvr%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b7a92beb4be2fff9a52e57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221310%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETicker%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fnvr-stock%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENVR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESector%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EConsumer%20Discretionary%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReturn%20last%2012%20months%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E12.5%25%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETransDigm%20Group%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221604%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22tdg%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b7ab517bb3f854015d6cde%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221312%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETicker%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Ftdg-stock%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETDG%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESector%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn