mp%20administration%20on%20Sunday%20in%20what%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20early%20sign%20of%20power%20struggles%20to%20come.%20The%20pushback%20came%20from%20Kash%20Patel%2C%20who%20took%20over%20as%20the%20ninth%20director%20of%20the%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(FBI)%20on%20Saturday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel%20has%20reportedly%20asked%20all%20FBI%20employees%20to%20%26quot%3Bpause%20any%20responses%26quot%3B%20to%20Musk's%20email%20ultimatum%20to%20federal%20workers%20that%20he%20sent%20as%20part%20of%20his%20supposedly%20unofficial%20role%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%20(DOGE).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFBI%20personnel%20may%20have%20received%20an%20email%20from%20OPM%20requesting%20information.%20The%20FBI%2C%20through%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20Director%2C%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20all%20of%20our%20review%20processes%2C%20and%20will%20conduct%20reviews%20in%20accordance%20with%20FBI%20procedures.%20When%20and%20if%20further%20information%20is%20required%2C%20we%20will%20coordinate%20the%20responses.%20For%20now%2C%20please%20pause%20any%20responses%2C%26quot%3B%20Patel%20told%20his%20staff%20in%20an%20email%2C%20according%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20Follow%2C%20No%20Index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FKenDilanianNBC%2Fstatus%2F1893479494079410229%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMusk's%20Ultimatum%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20billionaire%20advisor%20Musk%20on%20Saturday%20said%20that%20all%20US%20federal%20employees%20must%20justify%20their%20work%20or%20lose%20their%20jobs%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20president%20pushed%20him%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bmore%20aggressive%26quot%3B%20in%20slashing%20government%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20federal%20employees%20will%20shortly%20receive%20an%20email%20requesting%20to%20understand%20what%20they%20got%20done%20last%20week.%20Failure%20to%20respond%20will%20be%20taken%20as%20a%20resignation%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20AFP%20report%2C%20federal%20workers%20were%20asked%20to%20submit%20%26quot%3Bapprox.%205%20bullets%20of%20what%20you%20accomplished%20last%20week.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20email%20came%20from%20the%20US%20Office%20of%20Personnel%20Management%20(OPM)%2C%20with%20the%20subject%20line%20%26quot%3BWhat%20did%20you%20do%20last%20week%3F%26quot%3B.%20The%20deadline%20to%20reply%20was%2011%3A59%20pm%20Monday%2C%20though%20the%20message%20did%20not%20say%20failure%20to%20do%20so%20would%20lead%20to%20termination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20--%20the%20world's%20richest%20person%20and%20Trump's%20biggest%20donor%20--%20has%20led%20the%20effort%20to%20fire%20swaths%20of%20the%20government%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20Respond%3A%20Agencies%20Tell%20Employees%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20AFP%20report%2C%20several%20federal%20employees%20said%20they%20were%20advised%20by%20their%20agencies%20not%20to%20respond%20to%20Musk's%20email%20and%20wait%20for%20further%20instruction%2C%20a%20recommendation%20echoed%20by%20the%20National%20Treasury%20Employees%20Union.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20so%20much%20work%20to%20do%2C%20I%20am%20not%20going%20to%20neglect%20actual%20patient%20care%20for%20this%20drama%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20physician%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Veterans%20Affairs%2C%20who%20received%20the%20email%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20later%20appeared%20to%20downplay%20the%20requirements%20of%20the%20request%2C%20writing%20on%20X%20that%20the%20bar%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20low%26quot%3B%20and%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BAn%20email%20with%20some%20bullet%20points%20that%20make%20any%20sense%20at%20all%20is%20acceptable!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740303180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fjs7e6q9o_elo-musk-kash-patel-reuters_625x300_23_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkash-patel-asks-fbi-employees-to-ignore-elon-musks-justify-your-job-mail-7775414%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tech%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk's%20%26quot%3Bjustify-your-job%26quot%3B%20diktat%20to%20US%20federal%20employees%20faced%20an%20unexpected%20backlash%20from%20within%20the%20Trump%20administration%20on%20Sunday%20in%20what%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20early%20sign%20of%20power%20struggles%20to%20come.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkash-patel-asks-fbi-employees-to-ignore-elon-musks-justify-your-job-mail-7775414%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Red%20Sea%20Chaos%2C%20Gaza%20War%3A%20How%20Somali%20Pirates%20Are%20Exploiting%20Perfect%20Storm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%202017%20when%20Somali%20pirates%20hijacked%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsomali-forces-ready-to-use-force-to-free-ship-seized-by-pirates-1670185%5C%22%3EComoros-flagged%20Aris%2013%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20their%20last%20major%20attack%20before%20a%20period%C2%A0of%20relative%20calm.%20Years%20later%2C%20the%20threat%20has%20returned%20with%20full%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hijackings%20of%20the%20Maltese-flagged%20MV%20Ruen%20in%202023%20and%20the%20Bangladesh-flagged%20MV%20Abdullah%20in%20March%202024%20confirm%20that%20Somali%20pirates%20are%20back%2C%20and%20they%20are%20exploiting%20the%20chaos%20of%20the%20Red%20Sea%20crisis%20and%20the%20ongoing%20war%20in%20Gaza%20to%20strike%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resurgence%20is%20no%20coincidence.%20With%20naval%20forces%20diverted%20to%20counter%20Houthi%20attacks%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20global%20attention%20fixed%20on%20conflicts%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Somali%20pirates%20have%20seized%20the%20opportunity.%20Intelligence%20reports%20suggest%20a%20growing%20nexus%20between%20these%20pirates%2C%20armed%20militant%20groups%2C%20and%20regional%20smuggling%20networks%2C%20allowing%20piracy%20to%20re-emerge%20as%20a%20lucrative%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20The%20Red%20Sea%20Crisis%20Gave%20Pirates%20A%20Free%20Hand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20late%202023%2C%20Yemeni%20Houthi%20rebels%20have%20launched%20multiple%20attacks%20on%20commercial%20vessels%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20claiming%20to%20target%20Israeli-linked%20ships.%20In%20response%2C%20Western%20navies%2C%20including%20the%20US%20and%20the%20UK%2C%20have%20ramped%20up%20military%20operations%20in%20the%20region%2C%20leaving%20other%20critical%20waterways%20-%20such%20as%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20-%20less%20guarded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20shift%20in%20focus%20has%20created%20a%20security%20vacuum%2C%20enabling%20Somali%20pirates%20to%20revive%20their%20old%20playbook%3A%20hijack%20merchant%20ships%2C%20hold%20crews%20hostage%2C%20and%20demand%20multi-million-dollar%20ransoms.%20Experts%20warn%20that%20piracy%20financiers%2C%20many%20with%20political%20ties%2C%20are%20now%20leveraging%20the%20ongoing%20geopolitical%20instability%20to%20re-establish%20smuggling%20and%20ransom%20networks%20that%20had%20largely%20been%20dismantled%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Hijacking%20Of%20MV%20Abdullah%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hijacking%20of%20MV%20Abdullah%20on%20March%2012%2C%202024%2C%20was%20swift%20and%20well-executed.%20The%20ship%2C%20carrying%2055%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20coal%20from%20Mozambique%20to%20the%20UAE%2C%20was%20sailing%201%2C020%20km%20off%20Somalia's%20coast%20when%20pirates%20struck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fishing%20boat%20first%20appeared%20on%20radar.%20Moments%20later%2C%20two%20high-speed%20skiffs%20carrying%20armed%20men%20closed%20in.%20With%20no%20naval%20patrols%20nearby%20and%20no%20armed%20security%20on%20board%20-%20since%20the%20route%20was%20not%20classified%20as%20high%20risk%20-%20the%20crew%20had%20little%20chance.%20Within%20minutes%2C%2012%20heavily%20armed%20pirates%20stormed%20the%20ship%2C%20firing%20warning%20shots%20and%20taking%2023%20crew%20members%20hostage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Officer%20Md%20Atik%20Ullah%20Khan%2C%20who%20had%20ignored%20his%20wife's%20concerns%20about%20piracy%20before%20the%20voyage%2C%20later%20recalled%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2025%2F02%2F22%2Fworld%2Fsomali-pirates-red-sea-gaza-dg%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20called%20the%20engine%20room%20and%20told%20them%20to%20cancel%20all%20speed%20limits%20and%20throttle%20to%20the%20maximum.%20But%20our%20speed%20was%20nothing%20compared%20to%20the%20pirates'%20speedboat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Rise%2C%20Fall%2C%20And%20Return%20Of%20Somali%20Piracy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomali%20piracy%20initially%20emerged%20in%20the%201990s%20when%20local%20fishermen%2C%20angered%20by%20illegal%20foreign%20fishing%20in%20their%20waters%2C%20armed%20themselves%20to%20protect%20their%20livelihoods.%20Over%20time%2C%20it%20evolved%20into%20a%20well-organised%20crime%20syndicate%2C%20targeting%20commercial%20vessels%20for%20ransom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20peak%20in%202011%2C%20Somali%20piracy%20led%20to%20237%20attacks%2C%20costing%20the%20global%20economy%20an%20estimated%20%247%20billion.%20More%20than%203%2C800%20seafarers%20were%20kidnapped%20or%20held%20at%20gunpoint.%20It%20took%20a%20combination%20of%20international%20naval%20patrols%2C%20armed%20guards%20aboard%20ships%2C%20and%20multimillion-dollar%20investments%20in%20regional%20security%20to%20curb%20the%20menace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20current%20geopolitical%20landscape%20has%20undone%20much%20of%20that%20progress.%20Security%20gaps%20created%20by%20the%20Red%20Sea%20conflict%20have%20given%20pirates%20fresh%20opportunities%2C%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20an%20effective%20Somali%20government%20has%20allowed%20them%20to%20regroup.%20Reports%20indicate%20that%20ransom%20negotiations%20are%20once%20again%20taking%20place%2C%20with%20MV%20Ruen's%20hijackers%20allegedly%20demanding%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgcaptain.com%2Fsomali-pirates-demand-10m-ransom-for-release-of-chinese-vessel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2410%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20vessel's%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShipping%20Disruptions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resurgence%20of%20Somali%20piracy%20is%20adding%20to%20an%20already%20fragile%20global%20shipping%20crisis.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jpmorgan.com%2Finsights%2Fglobal-research%2Fsupply-chain%2Fred-sea-shipping%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJP%20Morgan%20Research%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20freight%20costs%20from%20Asia%20to%20Europe%20have%20surged%20nearly%20fivefold%20since%20January%202024.%20Many%20cargo%20ships%20are%20now%20rerouting%20via%20the%20Cape%20of%20Good%20Hope%2C%20increasing%20fuel%20costs%20and%20delivery%20times%20by%20over%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imf.org%2Fen%2FBlogs%2FArticles%2F2024%2F03%2F07%2FRed-Sea-Attacks-Disrupt-Global-Trade%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIMF%3C%2Fa%3E)%20reported%20in%20March%202024%20that%20Red%20Sea%20trade%20volumes%20had%20dropped%20by%2050%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20first%20two%20months%20of%20the%20year.%20Delays%20at%20the%20Suez%20Canal%20-%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20busiest%20trade%20routes%20-%20are%20compounding%20supply%20chain%20disruptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world's%20focus%20on%20the%20Red%20Sea%20crisis%20and%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%20has%20left%20vital%20trade%20routes%20exposed.%20With%20naval%20forces%20stretched%20thin%20and%20pirates%20becoming%20increasingly%20emboldened%2C%20experts%20warn%20that%20unless%20global%20attention%20shifts%20back%20to%20maritime%20security%2C%20Somali%20piracy%20could%20soon%20return%20to%20its%20peak%20levels.%20For%20now%2C%20Somali%20pirates%20have%20made%20one%20thing%20clear%3A%20they%20never%20really%20disappeared.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740303060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-03%2Fsomali-pirates_650x400_41489514411.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchaos-in-red-sea-war-in-gaza-how-somali-pirates-are-exploiting-the-perfect-storm-7775300%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20was%20in%202017%20when%20Somali%20pirates%20hijacked%20the%20Comoros-flagged%20Aris%2013%20-%20their%20last%20major%20attack%20before%20a%20periodof%20relative%20calm.%20Years%20later%2C%20the%20threat%20has%20returned%20with%20full%20force.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchaos-in-red-sea-war-in-gaza-how-somali-pirates-are-exploiting-the-perfect-storm-7775300%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2222-YO%20Works%20Nights%2C%20Teaches%20Rural%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20Kids%20Internet%20Safety%20by%20Day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20young%20boy%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F350255%2Fchhavi-rajawat-sarpanch-mba-soda-village-rajasthan-water-roads-college-digital-literacy-help-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremote%20village%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20carefully%20places%20a%20VR%20headset%20over%20his%20eyes.%20Instantly%2C%20his%20world%20transforms%20from%20a%20modest%20classroom%20with%20chalk-dusted%20blackboards%20to%20a%20futuristic%20landscape%20filled%20with%20coding%20simulations%20and%20imm