span%3Ecrypto%20winter%20in%202022%2C%20Vic%20Laranja%2C%20a%20content%20creator%20and%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeme-coins-trading-doge-pepe-trump-melania-retail-investors-crypto-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ememe%20coin%20trader%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20said%20the%20market%20was%20still%3C%2Fspan%3E%20trafficked%20mainly%20by%20crypto%20enthusiasts%20who%20believed%20in%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20before%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20been%20just%20a%20drastic%20emergence%20of%20retail%20investors%20who%20see%20meme%20coin%20trading%20almost%20as%20a%20new%20form%20of%20gambling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPuckin%20also%20lamented%20the%20state%20of%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMemecoins%20are%20no%20longer%20about%20community%2C%20no%20longer%20about%20fair%20launches%2C%20no%20longer%20about%20aspects%20against%20the%20%5Bventure%20capitalists%5D.%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20memecoin%20industrial%20complex%20developed%20to%20be%20able%20to%20extract%20as%20much%20as%20possible%2C%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible%2C%20for%20those%20who%20invest%20in%20it%2C%20which%20is%20not%20what%20the%20idea%20was.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f6ea376c-d49b-4020-8ee6-2079b9a11783%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20casino%20opens%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Laranja%2C%20the%20first%20stage%20of%20the%20meme%20coin%20explosion%20took%20place%20around%20the%20time%20spot%20bitcoin%20ETFs%20were%20launched%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%202024.%20The%20resulting%20surge%20in%20liquidity%20stirred%20up%20risk%20appetite%20in%20the%20crypto%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20month%20the%20ETFs%20debuted%2C%20traders%20were%20introduced%20to%20Pump.Fun%2C%20a%20Solana-based%20launchpad%20that%20simplified%20the%20process%20of%20minting%20the%20tokens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%3F%20An%20%26quot%3Bexplosion%20of%20meme%20coins%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Puckrin.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Fmadcap-rise-of-memecoin-factory-pumpfun%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSince%2520Pump.%2Cbeen%2520published%2520through%2520the%2520platform.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWired%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20were%20nearly%206%20million%20meme%20coins%20launched%20on%20the%20platform%20by%20January%202025.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20ways%2C%20the%20launchpad%20helped%20do%20away%20with%20some%20nefarious%20behavior.%20Before%20its%20existence%2C%20Laranja%20suspects%20about%20eight%20out%20of%2010%20memecoin%20trades%20were%20%26quot%3Bhoneypot%26quot%3B%20scams%2C%20in%20which%20a%20buyer%20cannot%20sell%20their%20memecoin%20holdings%20once%20purchased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPump.Fun%20came%20into%20the%20picture%2C%20and%20they%20standardized%20the%20contract%20address.%20They%20made%20it%20so%20you%20had%20to%20revoke%20freeze%20authority.%20You%20had%20to%20revoke%20mint%20authority%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20that%20the%20developer%20couldn't%20just%20mint%20a%20billion%20more%20tokens%20and%20keep%20them%20for%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20protocol's%20design%20did%20not%20curb%20pump-and-dump%20schemes%20or%20other%20practices%20that%20have%20given%20meme%20coins%20their%20reputation%20as%20essentially%20another%20way%20to%20gamble.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.prod.website-files.com%2F653c0500b1821c63d5bfc34b%2F679bc639ab1e1c197b450b99_PumpdotFun%2520Jan%252030.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20class%20action%20lawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20brought%20against%20the%20firm%20last%20month%2C%20alleging%20that%20it%20is%20operating%20an%20%26quot%3Bevolution%20of%20Ponzi%20and%20pump-and-dump%20schemes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMemecoin%20trading%20on%20the%20platform%20has%20ruffled%20investors%20in%20other%20ways.%20For%20a%20time%2C%20it%20allowed%20livestreaming%20as%20a%20way%20to%20promote%20tokens%2C%20but%20given%20the%20wild%20extremes%20users%20went%20to%20in%20order%20to%20draw%20attention%20their%20coins%20%E2%80%94%20from%20nudity%2C%20guns%2C%20and%20suicide%20threats%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblockworks.co%2Fnews%2Fpumpdotfun-suspends-livestream-feature%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20went%20away%20in%20November.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20the%20problem%20in%20the%20space%20right%20now%2C%20with%20the%20insiders%20and%20the%20bundlers%20and%20the%20snipers%20is%20not%20so%20much%20about%20the%20bad%20actors%20in%20the%20space%2C%20but%20because%20of%20the%20way%20that%20the%20protocols%20are%20set%20up%20to%20launch%20these%20meme%20coins%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c40176ad-6430-4069-89ad-177cb5898d49%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20need%20for%20change%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Trump%20Organization%20launched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fdonald-trump-crypto-coin-paper-billionaire-meme-token-launch-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20own%20meme%20token%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20before%20the%20inauguration%2C%20some%20say%20the%20dramatic%20price%20swings%20blew%20the%20doors%20open%20for%20imitators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%5BInvestors%5D%20would%20have%20been%20somewhat%20apprehensive%20to%20launch%20a%20meme%20coin%20just%20because%20of%20the%20regulatory%20risk%2C%20the%20risk%20of%20getting%20sued%20and%20whatnot%2C%26quot%3B%20BCA%20Research%20associate%20strategist%20Juan%20Correa%20said.%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20now%20the%20president%20has%20done%20it.%20It's%20okay%20to%20do%20it%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20(BCA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-price-prediction-btc-crypto-meme-coins-market-forecast-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaunched%20its%20own%20meme%20coin%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20month%20to%20prove%20the%20speculative%20mania%20was%20peaking.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20frenzy%20stretches%20into%20the%20early%20days%20of%202025%2C%20exhaustion%20is%20setting%20in.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESolana%2C%20the%20native%20token%20associated%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fsolana-sol-cryptocurrency-memecoin-rally-blockchain-trump-digital-assets-regulation-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblockchain%20that%20meme%20coins%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20usually%20launched%20on%2C%20has%20dropped%20around%2032%25%20from%20its%20all-time%20high%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObservers%20also%20say%20there%20will%20be%20consequences%20for%20the%20market%20if%20meme%20coins%20proliferate%20at%20such%20a%20dizzying%20rate.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorrea%20said%20the%20tokens%20detract%20from%20more%20fundamental%20crypto%20assets.%20They%20are%20an%20%26quot%3Bextractive%20force%2C%20Puckin%20added%2C%20noting%20that%20profits%20made%20on%20these%20trades%20are%20rarely%20recycled%20back%20into%20the%20crypto%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20going%20to%20necessarily%20go%20into%20developing%20an%20innovative%20product%20that's%20going%20to%20help%20solve%20real%20problems%20for%20the%20world%2C%20which%20is%20what%20I%20think%20we%20all%20think%20crypto%20and%20the%20blockchain%20can%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Puckrin%20said.%20He%20said%20there's%20an%20estimated%20%246%20billion%20worth%20of%20crypto%20liquidity%20has%20been%20leeched%20from%20the%20ecosystem%20due%20to%20meme%20coins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20regulatory%20path%20ahead%20is%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2F2025-42%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20unit%20to%20combat%20cybercrime%2C%20including%20blockchain%20fraud.%20How