r%20of%20Commerce%20has%20pulled%20much%20of%20the%20information%20about%20its%20Equality%20of%20Opportunity%20Initiative%2C%20announced%20in%202020%20to%20%26quot%3Bhelp%20close%20race-based%20opportunity%20gaps%2C%26quot%3B%20from%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20happening%20in%20a%20vacuum%3A%20The%20right%20has%20been%20increasingly%20vocal%20in%20its%20opposition%20to%20DEI%20efforts%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20and%20Trump%20has%20put%20that%20opposition%20into%20overdrive%20%E2%80%94%20and%20in%20writing.%20He's%20signed%20executive%20orders%20seeking%20to%20root%20out%20DEI%20practices%20in%20the%20private%20and%20public%20sectors%2C%20including%20barring%20government%20contractors%20from%20engaging%20in%20them%20and%20asking%20federal%20agencies%20to%20identify%20corporate%20targets%20for%20potential%20lawsuits%20over%20DEI.%20The%20plan%2C%20according%20to%20Trump%2C%20is%20to%20stop%20%26quot%3Billegal%20DEI.%26quot%3B%20It's%20not%20clear%20what%20that%20means%2C%20and%20the%20underlying%20law%20hasn't%20changed%2C%20but%20it%20still%20makes%20companies%20nervous%20and%20has%20had%20a%20chilling%20effect.%20No%20one%20wants%20to%20be%20the%20government's%20target%20%E2%80%94%20or%20draw%20the%20conservative%20internet's%20ire%20and%20become%20the%20next%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbud-light-transgender-controversy-backlash-boycotts-history%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBud%20Light%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Agencies%20may%20be%20looking%20for%20low-hanging%20fruit%20to%20make%20an%20example%20out%20of%20in%20order%20to%20scare%20others%20off.%20And%20regardless%20of%20what%20the%20government%20does%2C%20negative%20publicity%20and%20social%20media%20campaigns%20are%20a%20threat%20in%20and%20of%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20business%20leaders%20may%20remember%20some%20of%20the%20vindictive%20nature%20of%20Trump's%20first%20term%2C%20such%20as%20the%20president's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tried-to-block-the-att-time-warner-merger-to-spite-cnn-report-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopposition%20to%20the%20AT%26amp%3BT-Time%20Warner%20merger%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reportedly%20partly%20because%20of%20his%20dissatisfaction%20with%20CNN.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20Bloomberg%20last%20July%2C%20Ken%20Chenault%2C%20the%20former%20CEO%20of%20American%20Express%2C%20cited%20it%20as%20cause%20for%20trepidation%20about%20a%20second%20Trump%20term.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fear%20is%20real%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaniel%20Kinderman%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Delaware%20who%20studies%20business%20responses%20to%20right-wing%20populism%2C%20said%20companies%20may%20regret%20cozying%20up%20with%20Trump%20and%20being%20quick%20to%20bend%20to%20his%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20the%20government's%20doing%20is%20so%20radical%20that%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20companies%20will%20be%20sorry%20that%20they%20got%20on%20the%20bandwagon%20or%20did%20not%20keep%20a%20greater%20distance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20reducing%20their%20risks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20domestic%20and%20foreign%20fronts%2C%20the%20perception%20of%20Trump%20as%20a%20loose%20cannon%20may%20give%20him%20an%20advantage%20in%20negotiations%20%E2%80%94%20acting%20unpredictable%20and%20volatile%20is%20a%20way%20to%20throw%2C%20say%2C%20China%20off%20balance.%20But%20for%20business%2C%20it%20can%20be%20challenging%20to%20navigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBusinesses%20like%20predictability%2C%20and%20that's%20not%20what%20they're%20going%20to%20get%20from%20Trump%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alex%20Conant%2C%20a%20Republican%20strategist%20who%20was%20the%20communications%20director%20for%20Marco%20Rubio's%202016%20campaign.%20%26quot%3BTrump%20is%20highly%20unpredictable%2C%20which%20creates%20a%20challenging%20business%20environment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20note%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20David%20Kelly%2C%20the%20chief%20global%20strategist%20at%20J.P.%20Morgan%20Asset%20Management%2C%20said%20that%20the%20policy%20uncertainty%20created%20by%20the%20Trump%20administration%20could%20slow%20economic%20growth%2C%20affect%20hiring%2C%20and%20stunt%20investment.%20He%20pointed%20to%20tariff%20threats%2C%20immigration%20crackdowns%2C%20federal%20workforce%20reductions%2C%20and%20federal%20budget%20uncertainties%20as%20areas%20where%20action%20could%20be%20cause%20for%20business%20hesitancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rapid%20pace%20of%20these%20moves%2C%20along%20with%20frequent%20reversals%2C%20court%20challenges%20and%20mixed%20signals%20on%20future%20policy%20actions%2C%20make%20it%20difficult%20for%20economists%20to%20assess%20their%20cumulative%20effects%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BAlso%20important%2C%20and%20even%20harder%20to%20analyze%2C%20is%20the%20potential%20for%20policy%20uncertainty%20to%20delay%20business%20decisions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20an%20automaker%2C%20for%20example%2C%20you're%20staring%20down%20the%20potential%20of%20steel%20and%20aluminum%20tariffs%2C%20separate%20tariffs%20on%20imports%20from%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%2C%20and%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20from%20trading%20partners.%20Plus%2C%20you're%20not%20sure%20what's%20going%20to%20happen%20with%20electric%20vehicle%20tax%20credits.%20It's%20hard%20to%20know%20where%20to%20begin%20or%20whether%20to%20make%20an%20investment%20at%20all.%20At%20a%20conference%20in%20February%2C%20Ford's%20CEO%2C%20Jim%20Farley%2C%20said%20Trump's%20moves%20had%20created%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20costs%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20chaos%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20CNBC%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Walmart's%20chief%20financial%20officer%2C%20John%20David%20Rainey%2C%20said%20the%20retailer%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20going%20to%20be%20completely%20immune%26quot%3B%20from%20tariffs%20on%20imports%20from%20Mexico%20and%20Canada.%20Tariffs%20on%20imports%20from%20China%20would%20likely%20affect%20the%20company%2C%20too.%20He%20said%20that%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bfar%20from%20certainty%20in%20the%20geopolitical%20landscape%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20Walmart%20hadn't%20calculated%20tariff%20increases%20into%20its%20financial%20expectations%20for%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20are%20tasked%20with%20laying%20out%20various%20scenarios%20of%20what%20might%20happen%20next%20%E2%80%94%20and%20reassuring%20their%20shareholders%20that%20they're%20prepared%20for%20whatever's%20ahead.%20Elaine%20Buckberg%2C%20a%20former%20chief%20economist%20at%20GM%2C%20has%20been%20in%20this%20situation%20before%3A%20the%20trade%20war%20with%20China%20that%20Trump%20kicked%20off%20during%20his%20first%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20I%20was%20doing%20scenarios%20on%20China%20tariffs%20back%20and%20forth%2C%20basically%2C%20until%20COVID%20came%20and%20took%20away%20all%20the%20attention%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20prepare%20presentations%20the%20night%20before%2C%20and%20they'd%20be%20updated%20by%20the%20next%20morning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuckberg%20pointed%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fqje%2Farticle-abstract%2F98%2F1%2F85%2F1869115%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1983%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Ben%20Bernanke%20(who%20would%20go%20on%20to%20be%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20Federal%20Reserve)%20on%20investment%20decisions%20and%20uncertainty.%20%26quot%3BIf%20there's%20this%20irreversible%20investment%20and%20there's%20uncertainty%2C%20you'd%20rather%20wait%20until%20the%20uncertainty%20clears%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20that%20means%20you%20should%20expect%20lower%20business%20fixed%20investment%2C%20which%20hurts%20growth%20until%20this%20uncertainty%20resolves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECongress%20and%20Trump%20will%20need%20to%20negotiate%20through%20at%20least%20one%20tax%20bill%20this%20year%2C%20as%20Trump's%202017%20tax%20law%20is%20set%20to%20expire.%20Conant%20pointed%20out%20that%20this%20fight%20will%20be%20more%20uncertain%20for%20businesses.%20Congress%20may%20look%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20raise%20revenue%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20from%20higher%20taxes%20on%20certain%20activities%20or%20by%20eliminating%20tax%20credits.%20That%20could%20make%20for%20some%20winners%20and%20losers%2C%20and%20pit%20various%20industries%20against%20each%20other.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20the%20business%20community%20is%20going%20to%20be%20as%20united%20this%20time%20as%20they%20were%20last%2C%20because%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20winners%20and%20losers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20businesses%20are%20benefiting%20from%20plenty%20of%20Trump's%20actions%2C%20uncertainty%20and%20all.%20He%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20halting%20enforcement%20of%20the%20Foreign%20Corrupt%20Practices%20Act%2C%20which%20bars%20companies%20from%20bribing%20foreign%20government%20officials.%20The%20Trump%20administration%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20more%20hostile%20toward%20unions%20than%20the%20labor-friendly%20Biden%20administration%20and%20take%20a%20hands-off%20approach%20to%20regulation.%20Still%2C%20the%20insecurity%20of%20it%20all%20remains%20a%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20in%20Washington%20for%2015%20years%2C%20and%20this%20is%20the%20most%20chaotic%20time%2C%20where%20there's%20so%20many%20surprises%20that%20are%20happening%20on%20a%20weekly%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nick%20Nigro%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Atlas%20Public%20Policy%2C%20a%20research%20firm%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20too%20much%20uncertainty%20for%20meaningful%20decisions%20to%20be%20made%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20Economic%20Policy%20Uncertainty%20Index%2C%20which%20tracks%20news%20coverage%20of%20economic%20policy%20uncertainty%2C%20has%20risen%20sharply%20since%20the%202024%20election.%20The%20National%20Federation%20of%20Independent%20Business'%20optimism%20index%20ticked%20down%20in%20January%2C%20though%20it%20remains%20well%20above%20where%20it%20was%20during%20the%20Biden%20administration.%20The%20National%20Association%20of%20Home%20Builders%20survey%20that%20tracks%20sentiment%20among%20homebuilders%20found%20that%20confidence%20fell%20in%20February.%20The%20University%20of%20Michigan's%20consumer%20sentiment%20indexes%20dropped%20in%20February%20as%20people%20began%20to%20worry%20about%20tariffs%20and%20inflation%20concerns%20bubbled%20back%20up.%20As%20Americans%20contemplate%20the%20landscape%2C%20optimism%20remains%2C%20but%20reality%20is%20setting%20in%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20bit%20unnerving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20corporate%20America%2C%20a%20pervasive%20sense%20of%20unease%20is%20setting%20in.%20Businesses%20do%20not%20want%20to%20call%20negative%20attention%20to%20themselves%2C%20even%20on%20what%20many%20might%20consider%20run-of-the-mill%20diversity%20programs.%20They%20don't%20want%20to%20become%20a%20target%20of%20the%20president%20or%20of%20angry%20people%20of%20any%20political%20persuasion%20online.%20Meanwhile%2C%20they're%20managing%20an%20outlook%20where%20it%20seems%20like%20anything%20could%20happen%20%E2%80%94%20an%20executive%20order%20here%2C%20a%20court%20battle%20there%2C%20an%20immigration%20raid%2C%20a%20new%20tariff%2C%20an%20axed%20tax%20break.%20The%20feeling%20permeates%20through%20consumers%20and%20workers%2C%20too.%20If%20the%20federal%20government%20is%20taking%20a%20slash-and-burn%20approach%20to%20its%20workforce%2C%20what's%20stopping%20business%20from%20following%20suit%3F%20Many%20companies%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecent-company-layoffs-laying-off-workers-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecutting%20their%20workforces%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Plenty%20of%20consumers%20have%20wondered%20if%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-how-shoppers-and-small-businesses-are-stocking-up-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshould%20stock%20up%20on%20stuff%20before%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20take%20hold%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-consumers-rush-buy-trump-tariffs-fuel-stockpiling-report-finds-2025-02-18%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20have%20taken%20action%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScaredy-cat%20capitalism%20doesn't%20mean%20panic%20mode%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20a%20scenario%20where%20everyone's%20a%20little%20insecure%20about%20what%20comes%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-dei-tariffs-taxes-business-uncertainty-scaredy-cat-capitalism-anxiety-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740302282000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b7aadd7bb3f854015d6ccb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-dei-tariffs-taxes-business-uncertainty-scaredy-cat-capitalism-anxiety-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump's%20bum-rush%20first%20month%20in%20office%20has%20left%20businesses%20scrambling%20to%20win%20over%20the%20president%2C%20avoid%20his%20ire%2C%20or%20simply%20figure%20out%20what's%20going%20on.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22estewart%40insider.com%20(Emily%20Stewart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-dei-tariffs-taxes-business-uncertainty-scaredy-cat-capitalism-anxiety-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22t