ment%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fkeanu-reeves-shares-exciting-update-on-constantine-sequel%2Farticleshow%2F118501258.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Openly%20Gay%20Politician%20Is%20The%20Unlikely%20Queen%20Of%20German%20Far-Right%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20openly%20gay%20politician%20who%20lives%20with%20her%20Sri%20Lanka-born%20partner%20in%20Switzerland%2C%20Alice%20Weidel%20was%20an%20unusual%20choice%20to%20many%20to%20lead%20Germany's%20far-right%20and%20anti-immigration%20AfD%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgermans-votes-in-high-stakes-election-with-economy-migration-in-focus-7775026%5C%22%3ESunday's%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20her%20legions%20of%20political%20foes%2C%20Weidel%20serves%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfig%20leaf%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20party%20that%20rails%20against%20asylum%20seekers%2C%20Islam%2C%20and%20multiculturalism%20and%20some%20of%20whose%20top%20figures%20have%20voiced%20revisionist%20views%20on%20Germany's%20Nazi%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20the%2046-year-old%2C%20who%20says%20Margaret%20Thatcher%20is%20her%20political%20idol%2C%20looks%20set%20to%20propel%20the%20Moscow-friendly%20AfD%20to%20a%20record%20result%2C%20with%20polls%20predicting%20it%20will%20win%20second%20place%20at%20around%2020%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgermany-election-will-olaf-scholz-be-chancellor-again-or-will-the-right-emerge-to-victory-7770699%5C%22%3EWill%20Olaf%20Scholz%20Be%20Chancellor%20Again%3F%20Or%20Will%20The%20Right%20Emerge%20Victorious%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20election%2C%20Weidel%20has%20basked%20in%20the%20vocal%20support%20of%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20key%20allies%20--%20especially%20the%20tech%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%20--%20as%20well%20as%20Hungarian%20Prime%20Minister%20Viktor%20Orban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%20sporting%20a%20pearl%20necklace%20and%20a%20trouser%20suit%2C%20she%20was%20the%20first%20AfD%20politician%20to%20be%20invited%20to%20a%20pre-election%20TV%20debate%20where%20she%20sparred%20with%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%20and%20his%20main%20rival%2C%20the%20conservative%20Friedrich%20Merz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20has%20contributed%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bnormalisation%26quot%3B%20of%20a%20party%2C%20said%20Der%20Spiegel%20magazine%2C%20after%20the%20AfD%20was%20long%20kept%20at%20arm's%20length%20by%20the%20majority%20of%20German%20voters%2C%20and%20protested%20against%20by%20thousands%20on%20the%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20Alice%20Weidel%2C%20the%20party%20has%20lost%20its%20horror%20for%20many%20voters%2C%20and%20Weidel's%20numerous%20TV%20appearances%20have%20accelerated%20the%20normalisation%20of%20the%20AfD%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fall-you-need-to-know-about-the-germany-bundestag-election-2025-7768395%5C%22%3EAll%20You%20Need%20To%20Know%20About%20The%20Germany%20Bundestag%20Election%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeidel%20in%20January%20took%20part%20in%20a%20livestream%20on%20X%20with%20Musk%2C%20who%20has%20enthusiastically%20supported%20the%20AfD%20as%20the%20only%20party%20that%20can%20%26quot%3Bsave%20Germany%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meandering%20conversation%2C%20they%20railed%20against%20%26quot%3Bwoke%26quot%3B%20policies%20before%20chatting%20about%20Musk's%20plans%20to%20settle%20Mars%20and%20Germany's%20dark%20history%2C%20with%20Weidel%20insisting%20Hitler%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bcommunist%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Uncrowned%20queen'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Weidel%20was%20invited%20to%20a%20private%20meeting%20with%20US%20Vice%20President%20JD%20Vance%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20Munich%20Security%20Conference.%20Vance%20had%20boosted%20the%20AfD%20in%20a%20blistering%20speech%20there%20in%20which%20he%20called%20on%20Germany%20to%20drop%20its%20long-standing%20%26quot%3Bfirewall%26quot%3B%20that%20aims%20to%20isolate%20the%20AfD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeking%20support%20from%20foreign%20right-wing%20leaders%2C%20Weidel%20also%20recently%20made%20an%20appearance%20in%20Budapest%20with%20Orban%2C%20who%20described%20her%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20future%20of%20Germany%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20election%20campaign%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20(Weidel)%20is%20the%20uncrowned%20queen%20of%20the%20AfD%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Wolfgang%20Schroeder%2C%20a%20politics%20professor%20at%20Kassel%20University.%20%26quot%3BHer%20visibility%20has%20grown%20enormously.%20This%20has%20also%20given%20her%20more%20power%20within%20her%20own%20party.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeidel%20was%20born%20and%20educated%20in%20western%20Germany%2C%20making%20her%20an%20oddity%20in%20the%20AfD%2C%20whose%20core%20voter%20base%20is%20in%20the%20country's%20formerly%20communist%20east.%20She%20later%20lived%20in%20China%2C%20working%20at%20the%20Bank%20of%20China%2C%20before%20moving%20on%20to%20Goldman%20Sachs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeidel%20first%20joined%20the%20AfD%20in%202013%2C%20the%20year%20it%20was%20founded.%20Unlike%20many%20other%20early%20members%20who%20quit%20as%20it%20became%20more%20overtly%20xenophobic%2C%20she%20stayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeidel%20represents%20a%20wing%20of%20the%20AfD%20that%20%26quot%3Baspires%20to%20an%20independent%20existence%20to%20the%20right%20of%20the%20conservatives%2C%20with%20the%20possibility%20of%20forming%20a%20coalition%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Schroeder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20West%20German%20and%20a%20gay%20woman%2C%20Weidel%20has%20had%20%26quot%3Bsome%20problems%20connecting%20with%20the%20ideology%2