pan%3EAGM-158C%20Long%20Range%20Anti-Ship%20Missiles%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(LRASMs)%20launched%20simultaneously%20from%20different%20platforms%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20Morning%20Post.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Lockheed%20Martin-built%20LRASM%20is%20a%20stealthy%2C%20subsonic%20cruise%20missile%20with%20an%20estimated%20range%20of%20at%20least%20200%20miles.%20Equipped%20with%20multiple%20guidance%20systems%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-force-pick-ellsworth-base-to-test-new-long-range-anti-ship-missile-2018-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ELRASM%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20features%20GPS%20as%20well%20as%20onboard%20radar%20and%20thermal%20sensors%20to%20home%20in%20on%20the%20target%20if%20satellite-based%20GPS%20is%20jammed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Chinese%20simulation%2C%20the%20US%20destroyers%20launched%20LRASM%2C%20which%20initially%20rose%20to%20high%20altitude%20and%20then%20descended%20to%20skim%20close%20to%20the%20sea%20to%20try%20to%20delay%20their%20detection%20by%20radar%2C%20the%20Morning%20Post%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20they%20were%20about%2010%20kilometers%20%5B6.2%20miles%5D%20away%20from%20the%20target%2C%20their%20radars%20malfunctioned%20one%20after%20another%20due%20to%20electronic%20warfare%20interference%20from%20the%20%5BPeople's%20Liberation%20Army%5D%2C%20and%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20receive%20GPS%20positioning%20signals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20point%2C%20the%20missiles%20switched%20to%20thermal%20imaging%20cameras%20to%20continue%20flying%20and%2C%20at%20a%20very%20close%20distance%20from%20the%20target%2C%20they%20suddenly%20rose%20up%2C%20confirmed%20the%20specific%20attack%20location%2C%20and%20then%20plunged%20to%20an%20extremely%20low%20altitude%2C%20successfully%20hitting%20the%20Chinese%20destroyer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChinese%20researchers%20claimed%20to%20have%20gleaned%20details%20of%20the%20LRASM%20from%20open-source%20intelligence%20and%20%26quot%3Blong-term%20accumulation.%20Yet%20even%20the%20Morning%20Post%20%E2%80%94%20owned%20by%20e-commerce%20giant%20Alibaba%2C%20which%20has%20close%20ties%20to%20the%20Chinese%20government%20%E2%80%94%20admitted%20that%20it%20couldn't%20use%20public%20information%20to%20verify%20the%20accuracy%20of%20the%20missile's%20depiction%20in%20the%20game.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a4108fc-180b-40ea-9811-198ab3248cfb%5C%22%3E'Humble%20brag'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lockheed%20Martin's%20AGM-158C%20Long-Range%20Anti-Ship%20Missile%20played%20a%20prominent%20role%20in%20a%20Chinese%20wargame.%20In%20September%202024%2C%20an%20F-35%20flew%20with%20two%20LRASMs%20on%20its%20external%20pylons%20during%20flight%20testing.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b758ed6630eb10385d1a9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELockheed%20Martin's%20AGM-158C%20Long-Range%20Anti-Ship%20Missile%20played%20a%20prominent%20role%20in%20a%20Chinese%20wargame.%20In%20September%202024%2C%20an%20F-35%20flew%20with%20two%20LRASMs%20on%20its%20external%20pylons%20during%20flight%20testing.%3Cp%3EDane%20Wiedmann%2FDefense%20Department%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20China%20would%20include%20the%20new%20LRASM%20in%20its%20wargames%20is%20no%20surprise%3A%20the%20missile%2C%20with%20an%20estimated%20range%20of%20at%20least%20200%20miles%2C%20would%20be%20key%20to%20any%20American%20attempt%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-taiwan-war-us-no-allies-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edefend%20Taiwan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20Chinese%20invasion.%20What%20did%20surprise%20Western%20analysts%20was%20that%20China%20felt%20it%20had%20enough%20knowledge%20of%20LRASM%2C%20such%20as%20its%20guidance%20systems%2C%20to%20model%20them%20in%20a%20game.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%20notable%20was%20that%20the%20Chinese%20government%20must%20have%20given%20its%20permission%20for%20Chinese%20media%20and%20defense%20journals%20to%20publish%20the%20results%20of%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Furl-hedge-fund-wargame-china-taiwan-invasion-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewargame%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20typically%20has%20been%20classified.%20When%20nations%20learn%20the%20secrets%20of%20enemy%20weapons%2C%20through%20espionage%20or%20other%20means%2C%20they%20are%20wary%20about%20tipping%20off%20the%20enemy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBritish%20naval%20experts%20offer%20another%20potential%20explanation%3A%20China%20is%20playing%20mind%20games%20with%20America.%20%26quot%3BAlthough%20framed%20as%20a%20'humble%20brag'%20with%20the%20loss%20of%20a%20PLAN%20%5BPeople's%20Liberation%20Army%20Navy%5D%20destroyer%2C%20the%20article%20clearly%20advertised%20a%20certain%20Chinese%20confidence%20in%20the%20inevitable%20arms%20race%20in%20which%20China%20and%20the%20US%2C%20as%20technological%20world%20leaders%2C%20are%20engaged%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Edward%20Black%20and%20Sidharth%20Kaushal%20in%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frusi.org%2Fexplore-our-research%2Fpublications%2Fcommentary%2Fhumble-brag-chinas-recent-wargame-and-its-implications%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eessay%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20Royal%20United%20Services%20Institute%2C%20a%20British%20think%20tank.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBlack%20and%20Kaushal%20point%20to%20several%20glaring%20aspects%20of%20the%20Chinese%20wargame.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20simulation%20assumes%20that%20the%20Chinese%20destroyer%20successfully%20jammed%20the%20LRASM's%20passive%20radar%2C%20which%20homes%20in%20on%20electronic%20signals%20from%20enemy%20ships%20rather%20than%20emitting%20its%20own%20waves%20that%20return%20as%20an%20active%20radar%20does.%20In%20fact%2C%20China%20has%20been%20developing%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-military-increasing-jamming-power-with-new-electronic-warfare-platforms-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emethods%20to%20jam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20passive%20radar%2C%20such%20as%20feeding%20it%20false%20signals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20PLA's%20claimed%20success%20here%20would%2C%20if%20true%2C%20have%20ramifications%20both%20for%20the%20survivability%20of%20missiles%20with%20a%20low%20radar%20cross-section%20(which%20the%20PLA%20is%20implicitly%20claiming%20the%20ability%20to%20track)%20and%20for%20US%20naval%20efforts%20at%20emissions%20control%20and%20the%20use%20of%20passive%20detection%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20RUSI%20researchers%20note.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20game%20portrays%20LRASM's%20GPS%20being%20jammed%2C%20which%20suggests%20Chinese%20confidence%20that%20it%20can%20defeat%20anti-jam%20features%20on%20American%20GPS.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20British%20experts%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-qq-com.translate.goog%2Frain%2Fa%2F20250104A06F8F00%3F_x_tr_sl%3Dauto%26_x_tr_tl%3Den%26_x_tr_hl%3Den-US%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EChinese%20social%20media%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%94%20also%20point%20out%20a%20curious%20omission%3A%20the%20Type%20055%20destroyer%20only%20used%20electronic%20warfare%20to%20stop%20the%20LRASMs%2C%20even%20though%20the%20ship%20is%20well-armed%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-shows-off-new-type-055-destroyer-during-massive-naval-parade-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHHQ-9%20and%20HHQ-10%20anti-aircraft%20missiles%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20well%20as%20a%20short-range%20air%20defense%20cannon.%20Yet%20the%20destroyer%20must%20have%20detected%20the%20LRASMs%20to%20jam%20their%20passive%20radar%2C%20and%20radar%20tracking%20would%20allow%20the%20crew%20to%20fire%20these%20interceptors%20to%20knock%20out%20the%20incoming%20missiles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20each%20LRASM%20has%20a%201%2C000-pound%20warhead%20that%20can%20devastate%20a%20warship%2C%20it's%20highly%20unusual%20to%20rely%20on%20electronic%20warfare%20alone%20and%20at%20such%20close%20range%20(only%206%20miles)%20to%20down%20an%20incoming%20salvo%20of%20missiles.%20Even%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20jamming%2C%20LRASM%20could%20still%20lock%20onto%20the%20ship's%20thermal%20exhaust%20via%20infrared%20guidance.%20A%20warship%20is%20also%20unlikely%20to%20rely%20only%20on%20electronic%20warfare%20against%20missiles%20that%20close%3A%20if%20jamming%20fails%2C%20there's%20no%20time%20to%20launch%20missile%20interceptors%20and%20hardly%20enough%20for%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouthi-missile-close-us-warship-close-in-weapon-system-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egun%20to%20track%20and%20fire%20at%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20multiple%20incoming%20missiles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBlack%20and%20Kaushal%20raise%20a%20truly%20Machiavellian%20possibility%20for%20why%20China%20is%20publicizing%20the%20wargame%3A%20Disinformation%20to%20undermine%20American%20confidence%20in%20LRASM.%20Precise%20details%20of%20the%20LRASM's%20performance%2C%20such%20as%20its%20maximum%20range%2C%20are%20classified.%20If%20China%20is%20modeling%20the%20LRASM%20in%20their%20wargames%2C%20then%20perhaps%20Beijing%20has%20managed%20to%20steal%20the%20missile's%20secrets%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20likely%2C%20conclude%20the%20British%20analysts.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20PLA%20%5BPeople's%20Liberation%20Army%5D%20was%20truly%20confident%20in%20its%20success%20in%20accessing%20sensitive%20data%2C%20it%20would%20have%20strong%20incentives%20to%20keep%20this%20private%20to%20achieve%20surprise%20in%20a%20conflict%20rather%20than%20alerting%20the%20US%20to%20the%20compromise%20of%20critical%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20Black%20and%20Kaushal%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20an%20MA%20in%20political%20science%20from%20Rutgers%20Univ.%20Follow%20him%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3ETwitter%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmipeck%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-chinese-wargame-hints-it-can-blind-a-cutting-edge-us-lrasm-missile-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740301382000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b7597b7bb3f854015d5c5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-chinese-wargame-hints-it-can-blind-a-cutting-edge-us-lrasm-missile-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20simulation%20China%20made%20public%2C%20a%20powerful%20Type%20055%20destroyer%20succeeded%20in%20temporarily%20blinding%20incoming%20US%20anti-ship%20missiles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Michael%20Peck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-c